             was indicted for <rs id="t18170115-123-off652" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170115-123-off652" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170115-123-off652" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170115-123-cd653" type="crimeDate">14th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170115-123-off652 t18170115-123-cd653"></join>, ten pieces of printed cotton, value 10l., and four pieces of gingham, value 1l. 10s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170115-123-victim916" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Pool
                  <interp inst="t18170115-123-victim916" type="surname" value="Pool"></interp>
